definitions.definition: ( Scotland , Northern England , Wales ) A waterfall or cataract ( torrent of water running over a rocky bed), or a ravine down which such a waterfall rushes.

main_definition: ( Scotland , Northern England , Wales ) A waterfall or cataract ( torrent of water running over a rocky bed), or a ravine down which such a waterfall rushes.

definitions.definition: A pool of water , especially one formed and agitated by the water from a cascade .

main_definition: ( Scotland , Northern England , Wales ) A pool of water , especially one formed and agitated by the water from a cascade .
